        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued May 1 at 8:16PM CDT until May 1 at 8:45PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 816 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Adrian, or 15
miles west of Vega, moving southeast at 30 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Adrian.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
